author: Paul Cullen
title: Coronavirus: Death toll in Republic now stands at 174
description: More than 130 deaths took place in hospital, including 20 in intensive care units
content:
The deaths of another 16 patients - 10 males and six females - diagnosed with coronavirus have been reported on Monday by the National Public Health Emergency Team (NPHET).
